comments: Great teacher. Very helpful and easy to follow. Class can be slow at times, but is fun. You will learn many things.
Her class was a lot of fun and she keeps it really interesting. It is definitely easy to get an A. I think this class is great for anyone who needs the credits.

She was late a lot. her lectures were boring. she was nice overall. the online tests are what made my grade and i got an A on the 10-14 page research paper. the final paper might seem long but it wasnt terrible.
her open note tests saves your grade
chill teacher. go to class do work, test are open note, give effort and you will get an A or atleast a B
She was really nice but I got really bored in the class.

Nice lady, she is very willing to help you and she will go out of her way to do so but only if you approach her first.. otherwise she wont even be aware of you. tests are online=all open note. class can be easy if you are really proactive about the material.. shes kindof all over the place, disorganized, hard to follow, not clear in directions
